415
00:55:11,441 --> 00:55:12,999
Ne treba ti oruzje.

416
00:55:16,713 --> 00:55:19,045
Umalo da ih pokupimo kolima.

417
00:55:40,837 --> 00:55:42,327
Sta je, jebote?

418
00:55:49,846 --> 00:55:54,442
Mislila sam da ste mozda vi?
-Salite se.

419
00:55:58,254 --> 00:56:01,121
Mislila sam da ste vi to.

420
00:56:29,219 --> 00:56:31,653
Kakav pogled.

421
00:56:34,657 --> 00:56:41,062
l na vreme za zalazak,
necuveno.

422
00:56:47,537 --> 00:56:51,029
Slikacete nas ispod duge?

423
00:56:57,781 --> 00:56:59,681
lzvoli.

424
00:57:02,685 --> 00:57:05,415
Samo da slikam?

425
00:57:08,691 --> 00:57:13,924
Preziveli smo trag i
medeni mesec.

426
00:58:28,738 --> 00:58:33,232
Tamo ima podmorskih
pecina. -Ne brini za to.

