40 dolara i ne dugujes 20.

429
00:58:47,323 --> 00:58:49,416
lmam planove. -Kakve?

430
00:58:50,026 --> 00:58:51,618
Planove u sumi.

431
00:58:52,629 --> 00:58:55,826
Ako ne znas da vozis kajak.
